data.description: This move in ready Forest Run home offers a July 2023 roof, June 2019 HVAC, natural gas as of June 2020, NO city taxes and an award winning school district! Let the rocking chair front porch welcome you home. Enter inside to find hardwood flooring that leads past the formal dining room into the comfortable living room finished with a tall vaulted ceiling and cozy natural gas log fireplace. Off the living room you have the kitchen complete with a decorative tile backsplash, new microwave and stove, and a convenient breakfast nook for quick meals. Enjoy the outdoors from the screened-in porch, hosting cookouts on the back patio or sharing stories with friends around the fire pit in the yard. A detached shed built in August of 2022 is ready to aid in your home or garden projects. At the end of your day retreat to the first floor primary bedroom that has new carpet and an en suite bathroom with a dual sink vanity, walk-in shower and separate garden tub. Two spare bedrooms on the first floor offer guests a private space of their own or allow for an in-home office space. Head upstairs to find the fourth bedroom having a private bathroom with walk-in shower. This property is perfectly located just minutes from Historic Downtown New Bern while a quick commute to MCAS Cherry Point in Havelock and North Carolina's Crystal Coast beaches. Contact us today for your private showing!
